      <title>韩国渡轮灾难十年后，母亲们在舞台上表达悲伤</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/ten-years-after-south-korean-ferry-disaster-mothers-express-their-grief-stage-2024-04-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[李美京 (Lee Mi-kyung) 的儿子是 10 年前在韩国世越号渡轮灾难中丧生的 250 名儿童之一，对于他来说，应对悲伤和愤怒是极其困难的。她在舞台上努力克服痛苦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/ten-years-after-south-korean-ferry-disaster-mothers-express-their-grief-stage-2024-04-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 07:09:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚检察官撤销亿万富翁福雷斯特对梅塔的指控</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/australian-prosecutors-drop-billionaire-forrests-case-against-meta-2024-04-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚检察官已终止对矿业巨头安德鲁·福雷斯特 (Andrew Forrest) 对 Meta 的刑事起诉，他称 Facebook 上有数千个以他的头像为特征的诈骗加密货币广告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/australian-prosecutors-drop-billionaire-forrests-case-against-meta-2024-04-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 06:13:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>太平洋影响力争夺中美中关注所罗门群岛选举</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-election-watched-by-us-china-amid-pacific-influence-contest-2024-04-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[所罗门群岛的全国选举是自总理玛纳西·索加瓦雷与北京签署安全协议以来的首次选举，人们将于下周关注其是否有可能撼动中美在南太平洋的竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-election-watched-by-us-china-amid-pacific-influence-contest-2024-04-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 05:16:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>缅甸边境重镇沦陷后，大批人继续逃往泰国</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/exodus-thailand-continues-after-fall-key-myanmar-border-town-2024-04-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五早些时候，一群人在边境口岸排队逃离缅甸，其中一些人担心遭到空袭。一天前，泰国附近具有重要战略意义的苗瓦迪镇被日益强大的反军政府抵抗力量攻陷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/exodus-thailand-continues-after-fall-key-myanmar-border-town-2024-04-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 05:06:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本家庭通胀预期上升，加息空间打开</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/about-83-japan-households-see-price-rises-1-year-now-survey-shows-2024-04-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行周五的一项调查显示，截至 3 月初的三个月内，日本家庭的通胀预期有所上升，为今年再次加息留下了空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/about-83-japan-households-see-price-rises-1-year-now-survey-shows-2024-04-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 04:40:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中日海警在东海争议海域巡逻</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-japan-coast-guards-patrol-disputed-east-china-sea-waters-2024-04-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国海警周五表示，它在东海钓鱼岛（日本也称为尖阁诸岛）的“领海”进行巡逻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-japan-coast-guards-patrol-disputed-east-china-sea-waters-2024-04-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 04:38:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国、日本、美国在朝鲜威胁下举行海军演习</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-japan-us-hold-naval-drills-amid-nkorea-threats-2024-04-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首尔海军周五表示，韩国、日本和美国举行了计划已久的联合海军演习，其中一艘美国航空母舰参与其中，以确保做好应对朝鲜核威胁和导弹威胁的准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-japan-us-hold-naval-drills-amid-nkorea-threats-2024-04-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 04:28:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰致力于在全球不稳定的情况下加强与美国的关系</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/new-zealand-aims-boost-us-ties-amid-global-instability-2024-04-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰外交部长温斯顿·彼得斯周五表示，新西兰正面临几十年来最不稳定的全球环境，他承诺在中东和乌克兰冲突期间加强与美国的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/new-zealand-aims-boost-us-ties-amid-global-instability-2024-04-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 02:06:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国央行变得更加谨慎，表示不急于降息</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-koreas-central-bank-holds-rates-battling-sticky-inflation-2024-04-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国央行周五表示，在该银行将政策利率稳定在 15 年来的高位后，通胀前景和出口强劲的不确定性加大，不利于近期降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-koreas-central-bank-holds-rates-battling-sticky-inflation-2024-04-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 01:01:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国央行如预期维持利率稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-central-bank-keeps-rates-steady-expected-2024-04-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国央行周五将利率维持在 15 年来的高位，因为顽固的通胀和强劲的出口增长使政策制定者有理由推迟宽松政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-central-bank-keeps-rates-steady-expected-2024-04-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 00:55:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
